ar.", "Vi kommer til \u00e5 savne Harald, og takker for at vi var s\u00e5 heldige \u00e5 bli kjent og fikk arbeide sammen med ham. Vi lyser fred over Haralds minne", "For arbeidskameratene p\u00e5 Nidar", "Torstein H\u00e5rsaker"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c5dfc2e7f416be5b921f9944008ad178acd28d9637dead957755930fd24c5514"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-24T20:13:03.000Z"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7bee5d1ca277f3f5e14da7be223ab727a22899dd.jpg?595fbfca"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Minneord: Harald Simensen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7bee5d1ca277f3f5e14da7be223ab727a22899dd"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Minneord"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Minneord"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "nidar"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["heidi", "sollia", "tordenskjolds", "\u00f8rskogfjellet"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "harald simensen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "folk"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Minneord: Harald Simensen"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/folk/2015/11/06/Minneord-Harald-Simensen-11778892.ece"}, {"field": "pageclass", "value": ["article"]}, {"field": "publishtime", "value": "2015-11-06T13:03:48.000Z"}, {"field": "recs-articleid", "value": "11778892"}, {"field": "recs-category-ty